        <h3>Bank Soal HOTS</h3>
        <p>Latihan soal C4-C6 untuk melatih nalar kritis siswa.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='card'>
        <div style='width: 50px; height: 50px; background: #ecfeff; color: var(--primary); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;'><i class='fas fa-rocket fa-lg'/></div>
        <h3>EdTech Tools</h3>
        <p>Tutorial AI dan platform pembelajaran interaktif.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='ai-feed-section'>
     <div style='text-align: left;'>
        <span style='background: #ecfeff; color: #0891b2; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 2px;'>AI CURATED FEED</span>
        <h2 style='font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; margin-top: 16px;'>Berita &amp; <span style='color: var(--primary);'>Referensi AI.</span></h2>
        <div style='display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 32px; margin-top: 40px;'>
           <!-- Mock AI Items -->
           <div style='padding: 32px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;'>
              <h4 style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>Inovasi Pembelajaran IPS 2026</h4>
              <p style='font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary);'>Eksplorasi Metaverse dalam memahami sejarah lokal secara imersif.</p>
           </div>
           <div style='padding: 32px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;'>
              <h4 style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>Update ChatGPT untuk Guru</h4>
              <p style='font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary);'>Cara aman menggunakan AI untuk menyusun administrasi kelas.</p>
           </div>
        </div>
     </div>
  </section>
</b:if>

<div class='container' style='max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px;'>
  <b:section class='main' id='main' showaddelement='yes'>
     <b:widget id='Blog1' locked='true' title='Postingan Blog' type='Blog' version='2' visible='true'>
        <b:includable id='main' var='this'>
           <b:loop values='data:posts' var='post'>
              <article class='post-card'>
                 <b:if cond='data:post.featuredImage'>
                    <img expr:src='data:post.featuredImage.url' style='width: 100%; height: 350px; object-fit: cover;'/>
                 </b:if>
                 <div class='post-card-content'>
                    <h2 style='font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 900;'><a expr:href='data:post.url' style='color: inherit;'><data:post.title/></a></h2>
                    <p style='color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 20px 0;'><data:post.snippet/></p>
                    <div style='display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; pt: 20px;'>
                       <a expr:href='data:post.url' style='font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary);'>Baca Selengkapnya</a>
                       <div style='display: flex; gap: 12px;'>
                          <a expr:href='&quot;https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=&quot; + data:post.url' style='color: #1877F2;' target='_blank'><i class='fab fa-facebook'/></a>
                          <a expr:href='&quot;https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=&quot; + data:post.url' style='color: #1DA1F2;' target='_blank'><i class='fab fa-twitter'/></a>
                          <a expr:href='&quot;https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=&quot; + data:post.url' style='color: #25D366;' target='_blank'><i class='fab fa-whatsapp'/></a>
                       </div>
                    </div>
                 </div>
              </article>
           </b:loop>
        </b:includable>
     </b:widget>
  </b:section>
</div>

